title: OpenBSD 5.5/i386 (incl. OpenSSL security fixes)
description:
This is OpenBSD 5.5/i386 (32-bit x86)

Built from CVS release sources. Official release date is 2014-05-01.

***--------------------------------------------------------------------***
*** THIS RELEASE CONTAINS FIXES for the DREADED OpenSSL Heartbleed bug ***
***--------------------------------------------------------------------***

ISO File size: 561,692,672 bytes
MD5 (openbsd-5.5-i386.iso) = 23d17a64765443d61f905d0c8ed45792

CD is bootable and contains the entire x86 distribution + complete sources.

New features in OpenBSD 5.5: see www.openbsd.org/55.html
